Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/tigabelas/dotvim.git ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

Create symbolic links:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/tmux.conf ~/.tmux.conf


Dont forget to add Powerline fonts, please see blog
https://rnestler.github.io/setting-up-airline-vim.html

Set the terminal font to Meslo LG S Powerline Reguler, by right click in the
terminal and choose Custom Fonts
